    "Stocks Buyout: Buyout of stocks is a scenario where investors acquire the original or failed company agreeing on a lower percentage of stocks buyout such that the failed company can exit without any debt and investors can take advantage of rectifying the market with ease.",
    "In order to measure the business loss, the buyout stock price should be closer to the market value. 4.",
    "Liquidity Measure: As the name suggests, liquidity measure is nothing but the amount of available cash which can be used for business purposes within a short duration of time.",
